<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM2.6">
<l>ātiyantama ṉantamaṟputa māṉavāṉavar tampirāṉ</l>
<l>pātamāmalar cūṭumpattiyi lātapāvika ḷuyntiṭat</l>
<l>tītilnaṉṉeṟi kāṭṭiyeṅkun tirintaraṅkaṉem māṉukkē</l>
<l>kātalceytoṇṭark keppiṟappiluṅ kātalceyyumeṉ ṉeñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart will love in all [my] births</l>
<l>the servants who love solely our Father Raṅga,</l>
<l>wandering everywhere,</l>
<l>showing the good path devoid of evil</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the sinners –</l>
<l rend="indent">who are without the devotion [that consists in] bearing [on their heads]</l>
<l rend="indent">the great lotus feet of the Lord of the celestial beings,</l>
<l rend="indent">who is the Beginning, the End, Infinity, a Marvel -</l>
<l>are redeemed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
